{"tid":593612,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩打電話去叫個外賣自取..","createTime":"2018-03-15T06:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T12:58:31.000Z","uid":156688,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e389cd9b46d2834b62c4bad35557f1637f5f8540","tid":593612,"uid":156688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"餓左成日都唔知食咩好，又懶得煮<br />\n咁就上OpenRice睇樓下有咩食可以買返上樓<br />\n睇岩左有間小食鋪就諗諗下食個營多都唔錯<br />\n咁就打電話去叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽電話：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喂？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喂，你好，係咪XX（鋪名）呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我想要個撈麵餐架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：要3點先有，我地鋪開3點架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哦，咁好啦。<br />\n<br />\n之後就收左線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/144210_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F144210_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=74917958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我收左線之後真係黑人問號<br />\n明明睇住個餐牌寫住2點鐘開始有餐叫<br />\n但你又話3點先開始營業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n媽呀，好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a6b91da8a31856b5b612c9e329f2be287819e1","tid":593612,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"人哋食淨三點鐘咪賣俾你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286740862b1382cfff9b419ef3e8e7293245e88b","tid":593612,"uid":72688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:50:14.000Z","msg":"員工餐"},{"pid":"27908a08a503fcd5c04b9fca4441dd6c718c8769","tid":593612,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"比狗食架喎"},{"pid":"4325f01192757bcd7e2d395c4ed9709e8e50300a","tid":593612,"uid":53730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"你係打格仔就打好啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLikes慧食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832dbe50fd3ce37a710b24d8872ff7aa77d0087f","tid":593612,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜鳩"},{"pid":"8d97cf9adfb412dc4a6983540066bf7d52c5cf70","tid":593612,"uid":156688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4325f01192757bcd7e2d395c4ed9709e8e50300a","tid":593612,"uid":53730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"你係打格仔就打好啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLikes慧食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"打得好好架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咪捉我啦"},{"pid":"45f053e0a99777076c56a3bcdf6e383e915e609a","tid":593612,"uid":156688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77a6b91da8a31856b5b612c9e329f2be287819e1","tid":593612,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"人哋食淨三點鐘咪賣俾你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018